graph TD
    Start[User Login] --> Input[Enter Credentials]
    Input --> Validate{Valid Format?}
    Validate -->|Yes| Check[Check Database]
    Validate -->|No| Error[Show Error]
    Check --> Exists{User Exists?}
    Exists -->|Yes| Verify[Verify Password]
    Exists -->|No| Error
    Verify --> Match{Password Match?}
    Match -->|Yes| Token[Generate JWT]
    Match -->|No| Error
    Token --> Success[Login Success]
    Error --> Input
